"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?13/54/14177?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Hypokalemia (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?41/41/42640?source=see_link\">",
